Specification of experimental protocols 
Schema.org describes “types” of information, 
which then have “properties”.  
•  Example: “recipe” is a type that has properties like 
“cookTime”, “cookingMethod”, “recipeYield”. 
 
Bioschemas is working on specifications to 
improve the description of generic types in life 
sciences.
